/rotated-digits.htm\",\n      \"description\": \"Rotated Digits - Problem\\nMath Dynamic Programming Medium\\nAn integer <beginning of the code>x<end of the code> is a good number if after rotating each digit individually by 180 degrees, we get a valid number that is different from <beginning of the code>x<end of the code>.\\nEach digit must be rotated - we cannot choose to leave it alone. A number is valid if each digit remains a digit after rotation:\\n<beginning...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Strobogrammatic Number\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.simplyleet.com/strobogrammatic-number\",\n      \"description\": \"Solution\\nWe solve the problem by using a two-pointer approach combined with a hash table (dictionary) for the valid rotated digit mappings. The algorithm works by initializing two pointers, one at the beginning and one at the end of the string. = num[right]:             return False         left += 1         right -= 1     return True # Example usage: print(isStrobogrammatic(\\\"69\\\"))  # Output: True print(isStrobogrammatic(\\\"96...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777727086051},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough information about today's LeetCode daily problem. Let me provide the user with a comprehensive answer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🎯 今日 LeetCode 每日一题\n\n根据 LeetCode 官方数据，今日（2026年5月2日）的每日一题是：\n\n---\n\n### 📌 **788. Rotated Digits（旋转数字）**\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **题目编号** | 788 |\n| **难度** | 🟡 中等（Medium） |\n| **链接** | [LeetCode 题目页面](https://leetcode.com/problems/rotated-digits/) |\n\n---\n\n### 📝 题目描述\n\n给定一个整数 `n`（1 ≤ n ≤ 10000），统计在范围 `[1, n]` 内有多少个 **\"好数字\"（good number）**。\n\n**好数字的定义：**\n将数字的每一位单独旋转 180° 后，得到的新数字**每一位仍然是有效数字**，且新数字与原数字**不同**。\n\n**旋转规则：**\n| 原数字 | 旋转后 |\n|--------|--------|\n| 0 | 0 |\n| 1 | 1 |\n| 2 | 5 |\n| 5 | 2 |\n| 6 | 9 |\n| 8 | 8 |\n| 9 | 6 |\n| **3, 4, 7** | **无效**（不是有效数字） |\n\n**示例：**\n```\n输入：n = 10\n输出：4\n解释：[1, n] 范围内的好数字是：2, 5, 6, 9\n- 1 → 1（相同，不是好数字）\n- 2 → 5（不同，是好数字）\n- 3 → 无效\n- 4 → 无效\n- 5 → 2（不同，是好数字）\n- 6 → 9（不同，是好数字）\n- 7 → 无效\n- 8 → 8（相同，不是好数字）\n- 9 → 6（不同，是好数字）\n- 10 → 10（包含无效数字4，不是好数字）\n```\n\n---\n\n### 💡 解题思路\n\n1. **遍历**：对 1 到 n 的每个数字检查\n2. **有效性判断**：如果包含 3、4、7 任意一个 → 不是好数字\n3. **变化性判断**：如果不包含 2、5、6、9 任意一个（只有 0、1、8）→ 旋转后相同，不是好数字\n4. **同时满足以上两条** → 是好数字\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 核心代码（Python）\n\n```python\nclass Solution:\n    def rotatedDigits(self, n: int) -> int:\n        invalid = {'3', '4', '7'}\n        change = {'2', '5', '6', '9'}\n        same = {'0', '1', '8'}\n        \n        count = 0\n        for i in range(1, n + 1):\n            s = str(i)\n            # 包含无效数字\n            if any(c in invalid for c in s):\n                continue\n            # 包含变化数字\n            if any(c in change for c in s):\n                count += 1\n        return count\n```\n\n---\n\n要去挑战一下吗 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":2654,"output":696,"cacheRead":87803,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91153,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777727086061,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2afc1ad6-d1c1-424f-a0d4-deb5b42112f7"},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-05-02 13:23 UTC] 告诉我今天 leetcode每日一题是什么"}],"timestamp":1777728197049},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking again about today's LeetCode daily question. Based on the system time shown in the runtime, it's currently `Sat 2026-05-02 13:23 UTC`. \n\nI already fetched this information in the previous exchange - the LeetCode GraphQL API returned:\n```\n{\"data\":{\"activeDailyCodingChallengeQuestion\":{\"date\":\"2026-05-02\",\"link\":\"/problems/rotated